name: Naruto: What Kind of Starter Pack is 13 Years Late?
summary: After being killed by an EXCAVATOR, Takemi woke up in Konoha.To survive the upcoming calamities like Chunin exams, Pain invasion, fourth great ninja war, he had to work his ass off.Finally, after a WHOLE 13 years, he got the starter pack.When he saw the contents of his starter pack, he couldn't help but fall into deep thought.[Reward: Otsutsuki bloodline (1%)][Please develop it properly]Since then, the already chaotic ninja world became even more chaotic...
